                The authentication-context name correlates to the authentication context defined in
                the Elytron subsystem.
                Ex:
                <elytron-enabled/>
                <authentication-context>HsqlDbContext</authentication-context>
            ]]>
              </xs:documentation>
            </xs:annotation>
          </xs:element>
        </xs:sequence>
      </xs:choice>
